headline: Lennar Now Selling at Tuxedo Reserve, Hudson Valley's Brand-New Landmark Community
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, is now selling new homes at Tuxedo Reserve, a transformative new mixed-use master-planned community in New York's Hudson Valley.
